{"tid":1825121,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"強逼自己仔女去中國拜年既父母係咩心態","createTime":"2020-01-15T04:04:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-15T06:50:55.000Z","uid":249170,"like":31,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"bbeb726b6c172ef9a4c4a139b173220438bf882c","tid":1825121,"uid":249170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T04:04:50.000Z","msg":"今個新年仲強逼自己仔女去中國拜年既父母係咩心態<br />\n<br />\n一來場運動已經搞到香港同中國勢不兩立<br />\n中國藍絲多，上中國會比親戚歧<br />\n如果有去過遊行，一過關就有機會比人鎖<br />\n<br />\n二來中國肺炎，就算唔去武漢，過關關口直通車直通巴都夾雜好多武漢人<br />\n<br />\n本身屋企人係中立黨，自己冇事就咩都同意<br />\n但咁既時勢仲逼自己仔女去中國拜年係咩玩法?<br />\n<br />\n咁做都係為你好? <br />\n虎毒不吃兒? <br />\n教精你者?<br />\n袋錢入你袋?<br />\n<br />\n咪撚ON9, 佢做咁多野都係為自己好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3956672f48a26a7c61d779c0cc65d9f5d03c0ca","tid":1825121,"uid":55789,"like":18,"dislike":4,"score":14,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T04:08:09.000Z","msg":"你係咪搞錯哂 會俾人逼到自己返大陸果個先係戇鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41b7fb96966b6ec48e28c182f30c6dcfe8daa3be","tid":1825121,"uid":31863,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f3956672f48a26a7c61d779c0cc65d9f5d03c0ca","tid":1825121,"uid":55789,"like":18,"dislike":4,"score":14,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T04:08:09.000Z","msg":"你係咪搞錯哂 會俾人逼到自己返大陸果個先係戇鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T04:08:53.000Z","msg":"岩"},{"pid":"543d5fe17e47883de04f401a6425a9e27ba7b3db","tid":1825121,"uid":3501,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T04:10:40.000Z","msg":"我屋企人藍都唔會俾我地返大陸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n（雖然我地咁多年都唔需要去中國拜年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）"},{"pid":"9ea7692fcb49bfb053a0a5cac1ef1d9bfb57dcb3","tid":1825121,"uid":249170,"like":